snippet.title: The Occultist - First Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
First Gameplay Trailer of The Occultist.

The Occultist, a first person narrative horror videogame with hints of RPG. You will play as Alan, an expert occultist who is able to see and to interact with the other reality. His job is to investigate paranormal cases with different mechanics.
